"quote> , i <quote> </quote> ya:  <quote> Icyatsi </quote> na i <quote> </"
"quote> ya:  <quote> Ubururu </quote> . Urugero: Bya Ivanga ni <userinput> , "
"0 %S , 0 %S </userinput> : i Itangira Agaciro: ( <quote> Umutuku </quote> ) "
"ni na i Ibindi: 0 %S , iyi A Bibonerana Igicucu Bya Umutuku . Agaciro: Bya "
"Ivanga Kuri in i Urutonde 0 %S Kuri . A Gitoya Urutonde Bya Byakoreshejwe "
